OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGreen Party loses 'gender  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcritical' court battle     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Green Party discriminated against  
OL,6, former deputy leader Dr Shahrar Ali    
OL,7, during a row over his gender critical  
OL,8, beliefs, a court has ruled.            
OL,10,FThe court found the Green Party had    
OL,11,Fimproperly dismissed Dr Ali as a party 
OL,12,Fspokesperson because it had failed to  
OL,13,Fidentify any misconduct.               
OL,15,FThe Mayor's and City County Court      
OL,16,Fawarded #9,100 in damages to Dr Ali.   
OL,18,FBut the judgement upheld political     
OL,19,Fparties' right to dismiss spokespeople 
OL,20,Fwhose views differ from party policy.  
